author: Joshua Fechter
title: 30 things you didn't know about 'Star Wars'
text:
There's probably no other franchise in film history as packed with crazy and weird trivia for fans to obsess over and nitpick than "Star Wars."
But, even die-hard fans of the film series might not have heard some of these strange and fascinating tidbits.
And, with the looming release of "Star Wars: The Force Awakens" on Dec. 18, non-fans might want to get a leg up on their friends who likely won't shut up about that movie for weeks after it hits theaters.
Think you know everything there is to know about "Star Wars?"
Brush up on your trivia with 30 facts you may have missed about the beloved galaxy far, far away.
